{"tid":1254212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"70後高係最撚垃圾既人一代","createTime":"2019-06-24T04:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T05:19:18.000Z","uid":14908,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9efebb3f2a979084ac879530120dc0c1e33c1460","tid":1254212,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"70後就係最撚垃圾既一代<br />\n無之一，我屌你老母70後<br />\n食撚住樓價起飛香港起飛既年代<br />\n根撚本全撚部係搭順風車<br />\n自己成功少少就開始標籤80.90後<br />\n我屌你老母70後，70後就係最鐘標籤<br />\n你睇下60後有無標籤70後呀<br />\n根本就係70後帶起標籤文化<br />\n就算無做過，你無制止無屌鳩d frd<br />\n你同幫兇無分別<br />\n你lum左幾代既錢<br />\n你咪遠走高飛，咪撚搞呢代既年青人囉<br />\n但70後係要屌人，真係好撚憎70後"},{"pid":"0a15be75deef850b8120458b3aba9ffc144b3bbe","tid":1254212,"uid":27411,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"你咁樣咪又係標籤人，一碌鳩打一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本冇必要用年齡嚟區分人，仆唔仆街係因為佢做左啲咩事令你覺得佢係一個仆街，而唔係因爲年齡/世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02ed0ca9862f27d93b7cfde07c5dd89643c8f41","tid":1254212,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"各有前因漠羨人"},{"pid":"b42e5acd6f647313348690f433d52be5e784d107","tid":1254212,"uid":12503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a15be75deef850b8120458b3aba9ffc144b3bbe","tid":1254212,"uid":27411,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"你咁樣咪又係標籤人，一碌鳩打一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本冇必要用年齡嚟區分人，仆唔仆街係因為佢做左啲咩事令你覺得佢係一個仆街，而唔係因爲年齡/世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"連登終於有返啲正常人<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dcd07678225dfc8a6284b0dadb3d4967219c46","tid":1254212,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:57:16.000Z","ms